These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: whist, poker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, rock
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, chestnut
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, skiing
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
3. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Game   | whist     | poker     |
| Music-Genre   | rock     | electronic |
| Color   | grey | chestnut  |
| Pet           | horse    | chinchilla |
| Sport         | skiing   | golf       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, dannemann
The people have 2 different jobs:  manager, scientist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, epic
2 different pets are kept: dog, lizard
City: san-francisco, marseilles
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the person watching action movies is the manager##1
3. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
4. the scientist is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Cigar      | dannemann    | blend |
| Job           | scientist  | manager     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | action      |
| Pet           | dog        | lizard      |
| City         | marseilles | san-francisco     |

