2 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: ice-hockey, surfing
1. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Transport      | van        | tram     |
| City           | prague   | venice |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | horror    |
| Pet           | hamster    | rabbit    |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | surfing   |

