The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, tram
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
3. the bartender is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Job      | bartender      | pilot     |
| City   | new-york    | san-francisco  |
| Pet           | ferret   | hedgehog |
| Sport         | climbing | swimming |
| Transport     | ship     | tram     |

 